name: Overnight
detailedForecast: Snow before 5am, then snow and areas of blowing snow. Cloudy, with a low around 25. Northeast wind 17 to 26 mph, with gusts as high as 46 mph. Chance of precipitation is 100%. New snow accumulation of 8 to 12 inches possible.
